article.headline: Tesla Inc. stock outperforms competitors on strong trading day
article.body: Shares of Tesla Inc. The stock outperformed some of its competitors Friday, as Ford Motor Co. F, -1.36% fell 1.36% to $7.25, General Motors Co. GM, -0.15% fell 0.16% to $32.16, and NIO Inc. ADR NIO, +0.14% rose 0.14% to $21.47. Trading volume (28.5 M) remained 44.6 million below its 50-day average volume of 73.1 M.
